org.batfish.identifiers

Class FileBasedIdResolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.batfish.identifiers.FileBasedIdResolver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IdResolver
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FileBasedIdManager

    public class FileBasedIdResolver
extends Object
implements IdResolver
    Filesystem-based IdResolver that reads IDs from directories compatible with FileBasedStorageDirectoryProvider. Intended to be used together with FileBasedStorage.
